### Hadith 3:279

*Narrated 'Aisha:*

The Prophet said, "If a woman gives in charity from her house meals
without wasting (i.e. being extravagant), she will get the reward for
her giving, and her husband will also get the reward for his earning and
the storekeeper will also get a similar reward. The acquisition of the
reward of none of them will reduce the reward of the others."

